divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing in my horse pasture when I took the photo. I take random snapshots of the sky frequently. I didn't notice anything unusual until I had downloaded the photos into my computer. I am enclosing the original photo where there is a chemtrail (I think) and above that is the object in question. In the upper right part of the photo is a hawk which I left in because the original photo is untouched. In the other photo is the object that I greatly enlarged. I did not focus or do anything else to the photo. Feel free to do anything to the original you want for your own analysis. The camera was pointed in an Easterly direction when the photo was taken.
